Description :
The "My Juke Box v1.0", application was developed as an assessment for the module “Programming for Computing” at Sheffield Hallam University.
The application shows the use of the following components, ListBoxes, TextBox and Timer. In addition, it introduces secondary Windows and covers Scope e.g., Local and Global variables.
The application was created by Tasleem Bhatti (b7027314), student at Sheffield Hallam University.
